Represents a train-like entity that can follow a Scaffold path. This entity on it's own simply creates a marker that follows the path,
but in combination with a `phys_parent`, any Minecraft entity can be made to follow the path.

@attribute starting_path_node` "Starting Path Node" The path node to start at. Entity will teleport to this node on spawn.
@attribute speed Speed The speed to move at in blocks per second.